INSERT INTO
    fiskeridir_vessels (
        fiskeridir_vessel_id,
        call_sign,
        registration_id,
        "name",
        "length",
        building_year,
        engine_power,
        engine_building_year,
        fiskeridir_vessel_type_id,
        norwegian_municipality_id,
        norwegian_county_id,
        fiskeridir_nation_group_id,
        nation_id,
        gross_tonnage_1969,
        gross_tonnage_other,
        rebuilding_year,
        fiskeridir_length_group_id
    )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::BIGINT[],
        $2::VARCHAR[],
        $3::VARCHAR[],
        $4::VARCHAR[],
        $5::DECIMAL[],
        $6::INT[],
        $7::INT[],
        $8::INT[],
        $9::INT[],
        $10::INT[],
        $11::INT[],
        $12::VARCHAR[],
        $13::VARCHAR[],
        $14::INT[],
        $15::INT[],
        $16::INT[],
        $17::INT[]
    )
ON CONFLICT (fiskeridir_vessel_id) DO NOTHING
